quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,Nokuthi isijeziso sami siyisijeziso esibuhlungu
  15,51,Futhi batshele ngezivakashi zika-Abrahamu
  15,52,"Khumbula ngenkathi zingena kuyena ngakho-ke zathi, “ukuthula” yena wathi “ngempela siyanesaba”"
  15,53,"Izivakashi (izingelosi) zathi, “ungesabi ngempela thina sikulethela izindaba ezimnandi zomfana onolwazi.”"
  15,54,"Wathi (u-Abrahamu), “Ngakube ningilethele izindaba ezimnandi kulapho sengificwe ukukhula (ukuguga) ningitshela izindaba ezimnandi ngani na"
  15,55,Zathi (izingelosi) sikulethele izindabaezimnandingokweqiniso ngakho-ke ungabi ngomunye wabalahlekelwe yithemba
  15,56,Wathi (u-Abrahamu) “ngubani ongalahlekelwa yithemba lomusa weNkosi yakhe ngaphandle kwabadukileyo na?”
  15,57,(U-Abrahamu waphinde) wathi “nizokwenzani (lapha) Oh! Nina! zithunywa na?”
  15,58,"Zathi (izingelosi), “ngempela thina sithunywe ebantwini abayizoni.”"
  15,59,Ngaphandle komndeni kaLothi ngempela sizobasindisa bonke (ekubhujisweni)
  15,60,Ngaphandle konkosikazi wakhe esimthatha njengokuthi ngempela yena ungomunye wabasalela ngemumva
  15,61,Ngakho-ke kwathi lapho sezifika izithunywa ebantwini baLothi
  15,62,Wathi “ngempela nina ningabantu abangaziwa”
  15,63,"Zathi, (izithunywa) “Qhabo size lapha kuwena nalokho abangabaza ngakho”"
  15,64,"Futhi size kuwena neqiniso, ngempela thina singabaneqiniso"
  15,65,Ngakho-ke hamba nomndeni wakho ngengxenye yobusuku futhi ubalandele ngemumva futhi kungabi khona ngisho noyedwa wenu ozobheka ngemumva futhi niye lapho eniphoqwe ukuya khona
  15,66,Futhi salwenza lwazeka kuyena lelo daba ukuthi izimpande zalaba (abayizoni) zizonqunywa ekuseni
  15,67,Futhi abantu bedolobha bafika begcwele injabulo
  15,68,"Wathi\t“ngempela\tlezi\tizihambeli\tzami\tngakho-ke ningangihlazi.”"
  15,69,Futhi sabani uMvelinqangi futhi ningangihlazi
  15,70,"Bathi\t(abantu\tbaLothi)\t“asizange\tyini\tsikwenqabele (ekungeniseni) abantu na?”"
  15,71,"Wathi\t(uLothi)\t“lawa\tngamadodakazi\tami\tuma\tnina ningabenzi (bokuhle).”"
  15,72,"(Isifungo)\tngempilo\tyakho!\tNgempela\tbona\tbadideke umqondo bayaphuphutheka njengezimpumputhe"
  15,73,Ngakho-ke bathathwa ukukhala (umsindo) owesabekayo ngesikhathi sokuphuma kwelanga
  15,74,Ngakho-ke (idolobha lase-Sodom) saligumbuqela phansi futhi sanethisa phezu kwabo amatshe obumba olugazingiwe
  15,75,Ngempela kulokhu kunezimpawu kulabo ababonayo
  15,76,Futhi ngempela lona (idolobha laseSodom) lalisemgaqweni omkhulu
  15,77,Ngempela kulokho kunophawu kubantu abakholwayo
  15,78,Futhi izihlali zasehlathini (abantu baseMidyan) ngempela babengalungile
  15,79,Ngakho-ke saziphindisela kubona futhi ngempela wona womabili (amadolobha) asemgaqweni osobala
  15,80,Futhi ngempela izihlali zase-Hijr zaziphika izithunywa
  15,81,Futhi sabanikeza izimpawu zethu kepha abazinakanga (bazifulathela)
  15,82,Futhi babeqopha izintaba ukuze bakhe izindlu (bazizwe) bephephile
  15,83,Ngakho-ke umsindo owesabekayo wabathatha ngesikhathi sasekuseni
  15,84,Ngakho-ke akubazuzelanga lutho lokho ababekusebenzela
  15,85,Futhi asizange siwadale amazulu nomhlaba kanye nakho konke okuphakathi kwako kokubili ngaphandle kweqiniso futhi ngempela ihora liyeza ngakho-ke thethelela ngentethelelo emnene
  15,86,Ngempela iNkosi yakho ingumdali (wamazulu nomhlaba) iyisazi
  15,87,Futhi ngempela sikunikezile (amavesi) ayisikhombisa aphindaphindiwe (Surah Fatiha) kanye neQur’an enkulu (engcwele)
  15,88,Ungaphonsi amehlo akho kulokho esikuphe abanye phakathi kwabo njengesipho ukuze bazitike ngakho futhi ungabi lusizi ngabo yehlisela amaphiko akho (umusa wakho) phezu kwabakholwayo
  15,89,"Futhi uthi, “ngempela mina ngingumxwayisi ogqamile”"
  15,90,Njengoba sehlisa phezu kwalabo ababehlukanisa
  15,91,Labo abenza iQur’an ukuthi ibe izingxenye
  15,92,Ngakho-ke ngifunga ngeNkosi yakho! Siyobabuza bonke ndawonye
  15,93,Mayelana nalokho ababekwenza
  15,94,"Ngakho-ke\tmemezela\tngokusobala\tngalokho\tophoqwe ngakho futhi uqhelelane nabakhonzi bezithixo"
  15,95,Ngempela thina sikwenele ukubhekana nabenza inhlekisa
  15,96,Labo abenza omunye unkulunkulu (isithixo) basihlanganise noMvelinqangi ngakho-ke bayokwazi
  15,97,Futhi ngempela siyazi ukuthi wena siyacinana isifuba sakho ngenxa yalokho abakushoyo
  15,98,Ngakho-ke dumisa udumo lweNkosi yakho futhi ube ngomunye wabazithobayo
  15,99,Futhi khonza iNkosi yakho kuze kube ufikelwe isiqiniseko (ukufa)